Hello, today we experienced an issue where all the networktable values from the limelight were getting received as 0.0. We have confirmed through the limelight dashboard that there iss a valid target or that there was an x-offset present.

However, code-wise, I kept receiving both the tx and tv values as 0.0

// example print statement used to debug
System.out.println(NetworkTableInstance.getDefault().getTable("limelight").getEntry("tx").getDouble(0));

I’m honestly not sure what’s wrong and it worked fine before when we first programmed it.

thanks in advance.
